{"tid":2496360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！歐洲足協正在計劃立刻將皇馬曼城車路士逐出今季歐冠盃","createTime":"2021-04-19T18:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T19:21:51.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc9522a9c512cbbd2d154568e2d989ee21c5e5e","tid":2496360,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:53:48.000Z","msg":"香港時間4月20日，據多家外媒最新報導，歐洲足協正在計劃立刻將皇馬、曼城和車路士逐出今季歐冠盃。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉歐洲足協法律團隊正在評估將參加歐超賽的12傢俱樂部全部踢出歐冠盃的可能性。此外曼聯被立刻踢出今季歐霸盃也在計劃當中。<br />\n<br />\n  皇馬、曼城和車路士這三支球隊都闖入了今季歐冠盃四強，歐冠盃4強首回合將在香港時間4月28日和29日進行。"},{"pid":"91f8f31e23e4a281bd521448b40774b0aea0743e","tid":2496360,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:57:02.000Z","msg":"自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7ccde3eaf7a68ccc4b587a38c3baf337f477ae","tid":2496360,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"無提阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87afadaaa0d26fc095f7d77d0fb95c4092c9029","tid":2496360,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f8f31e23e4a281bd521448b40774b0aea0743e","tid":2496360,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:57:02.000Z","msg":"自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:58:39.000Z","msg":"係咪要賠轉播費果D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2118c4c53b284efae7ee98d2fc7348c0fe13a09","tid":2496360,"uid":64935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f7ccde3eaf7a68ccc4b587a38c3baf337f477ae","tid":2496360,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"無提阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\